[There are adequate vaccines for horses, cattle, most livestock and
certainly our companion animals. This illustrates the need to
vaccinate farm animals as well. It is very cheap insurance to prevent
human exposure. - Mod.TG]
[More information on the strain of rabies involved would be of
interest, as well as the control measures that have lead to the
marked reduction in rabies cases in Ontario. - Mod.MPP]
